## This document is to act as a rationale statement for most, 
## if not all of the actions performed in this script.

## SECTION 1 ##

Ensuring Auto-Updates are on can prevent a user from falling behind on important security-related updates. 
It's worth noting that this may not work for some enterprise environments, however, it is preffered for home users. 

## SECTION 2 ## 

# Bluetooth #
There is no purpose in having Bluetooth on unless a device is connected, as such, we will turn 
it off if there is no Bluetooth device present. 
At the same time, it is desireable that the end user can tell whether or not Bluetooth is enabled. 
